CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 31, 1962, pg. 24 reads: "Join Plunging State Mermen - Seen with Coach Ed Fleming (extreme left) are members of the Westinghouse High School swimming team. City League champions.  From left: Robert May, Danny Lloyd, David Montgomery, Clarence Reed.  The team won 12th ranking, statewide, during the recent state championship meet at Bucknell University, Lewisburg, Pa. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of members of the Westinghouse High School swim team, left to right: Robert May, Danny Lloyd, David Montgomery, Clarence Reed, and Coach Ed Fleming, standing on edge of interior swimming pool
